Package io.github.asdfjkl.jchesslib

Class PgnItem

java.lang.Object
io.github.asdfjkl.jchesslib.PgnItem
public class PgnItem extends Object
wraps information about a game within a PGN file. This includes the seven mandatory PGN headers, ECO classification as well as the index (n-th game in the file) and the absolut offset within the file.
